## Repository Workflow & Usage

- Scripts are Windows-focused; test locally with PowerShell before wiring to Stream Deck.
- Default launch pattern from Stream Deck “Open” action:
  - Program: `powershell.exe`
  - Arguments: `-NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -WindowStyle Hidden -File <script>`

### Common tasks
- Explorer paths to clipboard: see [Copy-SelectedPath.ps1](mdc:Copy-SelectedPath.ps1).
- ChatGPT with voice typing: see [Start-ChatGPT-Voice.ps1](mdc:Start-ChatGPT-Voice.ps1).

### Troubleshooting
- Execution policy blocked: add `-ExecutionPolicy Bypass` in Stream Deck arguments.
- Browser not found: ensure `msedge.exe`/`chrome.exe` is in PATH or use `-Browser default`.
- Nothing selected in Explorer: toggle `-UseCurrentFolderIfNoSelection` or ensure a selection.

